{"tid":1942240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府無能！巴西黑社會代政府宣布戒嚴","createTime":"2020-03-25T03:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T05:04:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a73dceb5ba3953b7a83f4c7f9728561f1ab0f0d4","tid":1942240,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:03:30.000Z","msg":"Brazil gangs 'order curfews to tackle virus'<br />\n巴西黑幫宣布&ldquo;宵禁應抗病毒&rdquo;<br />\n <br />\nCrime gangs in the Brazilian city of Rio de Janeiro are reported to have ordered curfews to combat coronavirus, saying they are taking action because<br />\nthe government refuses to.<br />\n據報導，巴西里約熱內盧的黑幫下令宵禁與冠狀病毒作戰，他們說他們正在採取行動，因為政府拒絕作出行動。<br />\n <br />\nResidents of several favelas (shanty towns) say they have received social media messages ordering people off the streets overnight<br />\n幾個貧民窟（棚戶區）的居民說，他們已經得到了命令，人們晚上不要在街上逗留<br />\n <br />\n&quot;We want the best for the population. If the government doesn't have the capacity to do something [about coronavirus], then organised crime will sort it out,&quot; said one message reported by the G1 news website.<br />\n<br />\n我們希望為人民提供最好的服務。如果政府沒有做某事[關于對抗武漢肺炎]的能力，那麼有黑幫就該跳出來<br />\n <br />\nPresident Jair Bolsonaro has been criticised for his lacklustre response to the outbreak, prompting protests in S&atilde;o Paulo and Rio.<br />\n賈爾&middot;博爾索納羅總統（Jair Bolsonaro）因對市場反應遲鈍而受到批評爆發，引發了聖保羅和里約的抗議活動。"},{"pid":"3ad695a8b613fdf294901ce3effd5cc5603307a6","tid":1942240,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"向太"},{"pid":"e03b974b0c24339159f63ecfbc9fa1b7b67c4d27","tid":1942240,"uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"幾時到老新宣布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446b7e6ff37d3b324c3ab9bad891c1